    <h1 style="text-align:center;">Free Medicare Plan Comparison — Vernal &amp; Uintah Basin</h1>
    
        <p>Comparing Medicare plans should not cost you anything. Vernal Medicare provides free, side-by-side plan comparisons for every Medicare beneficiary in the Uintah Basin. Use our online comparison tool or call for a personalized review with a licensed agent.</p>

        <h2>Compare Plans Online</h2>
        <p>Our Medicare plan comparison tool lets you enter your zip code, doctors, prescriptions, and preferred pharmacy to see available plans ranked by estimated annual cost. The tool is powered by Sunfire Matrix — the same platform used by licensed agents nationwide.</p>
        <p style="text-align:center;margin:1.5rem 0;">
          <a href="https://www.sunfirematrix.com/app/consumer/medicareadvocates/10569110/" class="enroll-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Launch Plan Comparison Tool</a>
        </p>

        <h2>What the Comparison Includes</h2>
        <p>Medicare Advantage plans (HMO and PPO) with estimated annual costs, Medicare Supplement (Medigap) quotes for Plan G and Plan N, Part D prescription drug plan comparisons based on your medications, pharmacy cost differences (Smith's, Walgreens, mail-order), doctor and hospital network verification, and extra benefit comparisons (dental, vision, hearing, fitness).</p>

        <h2>Personalized Help Available</h2>
        <p>The online tool is a great starting point, but a 15-minute phone call with Rocco can identify savings the tool may miss. We check for Extra Help eligibility, verify provider networks, and consider factors like travel patterns and upcoming procedures that affect which plan is truly best for you. Call <a href="tel:+14352195120">435-219-5120</a> or email <a href="mailto:rocco@vernalmedicare.com">rocco@vernalmedicare.com</a>.</p>

        <h2>No Cost, No Obligation</h2>
        <p>Plan comparisons are always free. Vernal Medicare is compensated by insurance carriers when you enroll — you pay nothing for our advice, time, or expertise. We serve Vernal, Naples, Maeser, Jensen, Roosevelt, Duchesne, and all of Uintah and Duchesne Counties.</p>

        <p>Related: <a href="best-medicare-advantage-vernal.html">Best Advantage plans</a> | <a href="best-part-d-plans-vernal.html">Best Part D plans</a> | <a href="plan-g-vs-plan-n-vernal.html">Plan G vs Plan N</a></p>
        <p><em>Source: <a href="https://www.medicare.gov" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Medicare.gov</a>.</em></p>
        
